name: Asian Inspired Two Fish Necklace
description: Beautiful agate pendant with two lucky fish. Red jasper and peridot chips to accent. Asymmetrical design. Gold fancy button as clasp.

name: Whale of a Tale: The Deep End
description:
A Whale of a Tale: The Deep End is a fun and animated description for two designs I have created, one being inspired by the deep end of the ocean, one the shallow. Think of the gorgeous shades of the ocean mixed with a fun metal whale and you have a great summer piece of jewelry. The pictured Deep End is made with a metal whale pendant, copper and brass in tone. The beads are a mixture of dyed agate, imperial jasper, and Swarovski crystals in capri blue. Clasp is brass metal toggle. Strung on waxed fireline wire. The details in the beads resemble waves and foam of the ocean. 

Length: 20 "

name: The Multicolored Bird of Paradise
description:
Bird of Paradise came to mind when I created his design. The metal bird in the necklace sits asymmetrical, left side. Vivid colors of imperial jasper and Swarovski crystal compliment the romantic shapes of the bird. Toggle clasp is delicate and curved. Metal spacers provide just enough contrast to the design.

Length: 20 "

name: The Heart
description:
Unique asymmetrical heart necklace, handmade. Brass aqua and red swirls go perfectly with Swarovski crystals in a vibrant aqua matte finish. Fancy brass button for clasp.

20" in length in photo above.

name: Yellow and Aqua Bird of Paradise
description:
The Yellow and Aqua Bird of Paradise is a similar design to my Multi Colored Bird of Paradise Necklace. This design uses dyed howlite in a raw shape, yellow banded agate nuggets , Swarovski crystals in black AB, and metal. Clasp is toggled design with a speckled texture. Exotic and different, it's sure to catch an eye....

Length: 21.5 ". Custom lengths available.
